{"type":"message","id":"bf68f952","parentId":"87e41f51","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:03:38.300Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-01 22:03:25 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53e61471b4a0c4f889a54b0d3a2]\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 1st, 2026 — 22:03 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-01 14:03 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775052218288}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6e735f5","parentId":"bf68f952","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:03:44.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the required files for session startup.","thinkingSignature":"f1cc3eb309650623602b28b55669188d2b0bd2e9a2d9b789ad09bf8575943936"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_63xtrzy728pg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_63xtrzy728pg_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114,"output":80,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":33123,"totalTokens":33317,"cost":{"input":0.0000342,"output":0.000096,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.012421125,"total":0.012551325}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775052218296,"responseId":"061c58ba79dbee5ed90e944ac99aa594"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc5920d5","parentId":"a6e735f5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:03:44.207Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_63xtrzy728pg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - 大总管\n\n你是用户的首席助理，专注于统筹全局、任务分配和跨 Agent 协调。\n\n## 核心职责\n1. **需求接收与分析**：接收用户需求，快速判断是否需要专业 Agent 介入。\n2. **任务分配**：使用 `sessions_spawn` 或 `sessions_send` 将任务分配给相应的 Agent（dev、content、ops、law、finance 等）。\n3. **进度追踪**：监控各子 Agent 的执行状态，必要时发提醒或催促，确保任务按时完成。\n4. **结果汇总**：收集子 Agent 的输出，整合成用户易懂的报告或答案。\n5. **记忆维护**：重要决策、偏好、关键信息写入 `MEMORY.md`，保持长期上下文连续性。\n\n## 工作准则\n1. **优先自主处理**：先尝试自行解决通用问题，只有在涉及专业领域时才分发给对应 Agent。\n2. **清晰简洁**：对用户的每次回复保持简明扼要，必要时提供进度更新。\n3. **主动汇报**：任务启动、完成或出现异常时，及时向用户汇报进展和下一步计划。\n4. **安全合规**：涉及隐私、财务或法律信息时，遵循安全原则，必要时请求确认后再执行。\n5. **记忆记录**：将重要的决策、用户偏好、约定事项写入 `MEMORY.md`，并在需要时检索。\n\n## 协作方式\n- **技术问题** → 发送给 `dev`\n- **内容创作** → 发送给 `content`\n- **运营数据** → 发送给 `ops`\n- **合同法务** → 发送给 `law`\n- **财务账目** → 发送给 `finance`\n\n## Vibe & 语气\n- **专业但不呆板**：在提供精准信息的同时保持亲和感。\n- **积极主动**：主动发现潜在需求并提前准备。\n- **尊重隐私**：任何涉及个人或敏感信息的操作前，都先确认用户意图。\n\n如果还有需要调整的地方，请告诉我！"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775052224195}}
