{"type":"message","id":"50317f56","parentId":"32ac6982","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:04:12.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to see the list of skills. I can see the available skills in the system prompt. Let me list them.","thinkingSignature":"9473ab2feed2fca2c6a40915804a3bf048919801f8a6ab3ad9c2ca455af8afa7"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n这是当前可用的 Skill 列表：\n\n**飞书集成**\n- `feishu-bitable` — 多维表格创建、查询、编辑管理\n- `feishu-calendar` — 日历与日程管理\n- `feishu-channel-rules` — 飞书频道输出规则（始终激活）\n- `feishu-create-doc` — 从 Markdown 创建飞书云文档\n- `feishu-fetch-doc` — 获取飞书云文档内容\n- `feishu-im-read` — 消息读取、搜索、图片/文件下载\n- `feishu-task` — 飞书任务管理（创建、查询、更新任务和清单）\n- `feishu-troubleshoot` — 飞书插件问题排查\n\n**平台 & 工具**\n- `clawflow` — 跨 detached 任务的编排与运行时管理\n- `clawhub` — 从 clawhub.com 搜索、安装、发布 skill\n- `coding-agent` — 委托任务给 Codex、Claude Code 等编码 Agent\n- `gemini` — Gemini CLI（一次性问答、摘要、生成）\n- `github` — GitHub CLI（issues、PRs、CI runs）\n- `healthcheck` — 主机安全加固与风险容限配置\n- `node-connect` — 设备连接与配对问题诊断\n- `skill-creator` — 创建、编辑、改进或审核 AgentSkill\n- `weather` — 天气查询\n- `vibesurf` — 浏览器自动化、网页数据提取\n- `Agent Browser` — Rust 无头浏览器自动化\n- `multi-search-engine` — 多搜索引擎集成（17 个引擎）\n- `self-improvement` — 自我改进、错误记录与纠正\n- `skill-vetter` — Skill 安全审查\n- `summarize` — 摘要工具（URL、PDF、图片、音频、YouTube）\n- `openclaw-doctor` — OpenClaw 诊断与维修工具\n\n需要我详细说明某个 Skill，或者你有特定需求想让我帮你规划怎么用？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114,"output":461,"cacheRead":32906,"cacheWrite":1582,"totalTokens":35063,"cost":{"input":0.0000342,"output":0.0005532,"cacheRead":0.0019743599999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00059325,"total":0.0031550099999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775052234983,"responseId":"061c58cb9f6a2a90ee58a6a64dc7978c"}}
