{"type":"message","id":"cad71a7f","parentId":"8d725a65","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:47:50.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image shows:\n1. The user ran `clawhub install feishu-multi-agent-manager`\n2. It returned an error saying \"Already installed: /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-multi-agent-manager (use --force)\"\n3. There's also a warning: \"Fix reachability first: openclaw gateway probe\"\n4. The user pressed Ctrl+C to cancel\n\nSo the skill IS already installed, but there's a gateway probe issue. Also the error says it's already installed, so the installation did work at some point.\n\nThe key issue seems to be the \"Fix reachability first: openclaw gateway probe\" message. This suggests the gateway might not be properly running or reachable.\n\n\nSince it's already installed, I should focus on the reachability problem first. Let me check if the skill has a SKILL.md file I can access to understand what's available, then address the gateway connectivity issue.","thinkingSignature":"9404ee331863d3934dd498737de621ac7cd18691123b41a4e85e3487fa2bcd80"},{"type":"text","text":"图片看到了。skill 已经安装成功了（显示 `Already installed`），但同时有个警告：\n\n> `Fix reachability first: openclaw gateway probe`\n\n这说明 OpenClaw Gateway 当前状态有问题，连通性检查失败。这个警告不解决，skill 可能无法正常加载。\n\n**两步走：**\n\n**1. 先修复 gateway 连通性**，在你的 Surface Pro 4 上运行：\n```\nopenclaw gateway probe\n```\n看看输出什么错误。\n\n**2. 然后再看 skill 有没有生效**，可以运行：\n```\nopenclaw skills list\n```\n确认 `feishu-multi-agent-manager` 是否在列表里。\n\n把两步的输出发给我，我帮你进一步排查。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5016,"output":328,"cacheRead":31568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36912,"cost":{"input":0.0015048,"output":0.00039359999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0018940799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00379248}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775054859807,"responseId":"061c630c8082fad6243248866b4de39f"}}
