{"type":"message","id":"62a5b41d","parentId":"f4d874b5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:51:52.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to configure a bot using the `feishu-multi-agent-manager` skill they just installed. Let me first read the SKILL.md file of that skill to understand what it does and how to use it.","thinkingSignature":"6176c18502df92861a0b7fdf0046e31d89ae27b98ff3a1fec02758047f33a047"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我先看看这个 skill 的说明文档。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x9584s9jf4gv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-multi-agent-manager/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":104,"cacheRead":37023,"cacheWrite":866,"totalTokens":38102,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0.00222138,"cacheWrite":0.00032475,"total":0.00270363}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775055108399,"responseId":"061c64048dacb396a15ddade8276b315"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0184e87","parentId":"62a5b41d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:51:52.988Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_x9584s9jf4gv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nid: feishu-multi-agent-manager\nowner_id: rfdiosuao\nname: 飞书多 Agent 配置助手\ndescription: 交互式引导配置多 Agent 系统，支持批量创建、凭证验证、角色模板\nversion: 2.0.2\nicon: \"\\U0001F916\"\nauthor: rfdiosuao\nmetadata:\n  clawdbot:\n    emoji: \"\\U0001F916\"\n    requires:\n      bins: []\n---\n\n# 飞书多 Agent 配置助手 🤖\n\n> 交互式引导配置多 Agent 系统，支持批量创建、凭证验证、角色模板\n\n## ✨ 功能特性\n\n### 1. 交互式配置向导\n- 像聊天一样完成配置\n- 询问创建几个 Agent（1-10）\n- 提供预设角色推荐\n\n### 2. 批量创建支持\n- 一次性创建多个 Agent\n- 自动验证每个凭证\n- 详细的成功/失败报告\n\n### 3. 飞书 Bot 创建教程\n- 7 步详细教程\n- 包含检查清单\n- 常见问题解答\n\n### 4. 预设角色模板\n- 6 个经典角色（main/dev/content/ops/law/finance）\n- 每个角色包含完整人设文件\n- 支持完全自定义\n\n### 5. 凭证验证\n- 自动验证 AppID 格式\n- 自动验证 AppSecret 长度\n- 友好的错误提示\n\n### 6. 工作区隔离\n- 每个 Agent 独立 workspace\n- 记忆文件独立\n- 会话存储独立\n\n## 🚀 使用方式\n\n### 启动配置向导\n\n```typescript\nawait main(ctx, { action: 'start_wizard' });\n```\n\n### 选择 Agent 数量\n\n```typescript\nawait main(ctx, { action: 'select_count', count: '6' });\n```\n\n### 查看飞书教程\n\n```typescript\nawait main(ctx, { \n  action: 'show_tutorial',\n  step: '1',\n  agentName: '大总管'\n});\n```\n\n### 批量创建 Agent\n\n```typescript\nawait main(ctx, {\n  action: 'batch_create',\n  agents: [\n    { agentId: 'main', agentName: '大总管', appId: 'cli_xxx', appSecret: 'xxx', isDefault: true },\n    { agentId: 'dev', agentName: '开发助理', appId: 'cli_xxx', appSecret: 'xxx' },\n    { agentId: 'content', agentName: '内容助理', appId: 'cli_xxx', appSecret: 'xxx' }\n  ]\n});\n```\n\n### 查看配置状态\n\n```typescript\nawait main(ctx, { action: 'show_status' });\n```\n\n## 📋 配置流程\n\n1. **启动向导** - 回复「开始配置」\n2. **选择数量** - 告诉 Bot 创建几个 Agent\n3. **选择模式** - 预设/自定义/全新\n4. **创建飞书应用** - 按照教程创建每个 Bot\n5. **验证凭证** - 自动验证 AppID/AppSecret\n6. **批量创建** - 一次性创建所有 Agent\n7. **重启生效** - 重启 OpenClaw\n\n## ⚠️ 重要：配置格式说明\n\n### ✅ 正确格式（对象格式）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"main\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"\n        },\n        \"dev\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_yyyyyyyyyyyyyyy\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"yyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### ❌ 错误格式（数组格式 - 不支持！）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": [\n        {\n          \"accountId\": \"main\",\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"accountId\": \"dev\",\n          \"appId\": \"cli_yyyyyyyyyyyyyyy\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"yyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**问题说明：** 飞书插件要求 `accounts` 必须是**对象格式**，key 为 accountId。如果使用数组格式，插件仅能识别数组中第一个元素（主账号），其余账号完全不会被加载。\n\n**自动修复：** v2.0.1+ 版本会自动检测并转换数组格式为对象格式。\n\n## 🎯 预设角色\n\n| 角色 | 职责 | 表情 |\n|------|------|------|\n| main | 大总管 - 统筹全局 | 🎯 |\n| dev | 开发助理 - 技术架构 | 🧑‍💻 |\n| content | 内容助理 - 文案创作 | ✍️ |\n| ops | 运营助理 - 用户增长 | 📈 |\n| law | 法务助理 - 合同审核 | 📜 |\n| finance | 财务助理 - 账目管理 | 💰 |\n\n## 📚 完整文档\n\n查看 [GitHub README](https://github.com/rfdiosuao/openclaw-skills/blob/main/feishu-multi-agent-manager/README.md)\n\n## 🔗 相关链接\n\n- [GitHub 仓库](https://github.com/rfdiosuao/openclaw-skills)\n- [飞书云文档教程](https://www.feishu.cn/docx/PYlXdsZoEoPPDbxyBRWc9HpRnIe)\n- [OpenClaw 官方文档](https://docs.openclaw.ai)\n\n---\n\n**版本：** 2.0.0  \n**作者：** rfdiosuao  \n**许可证：** MIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775055112981}}
{"type":"message","id":"91b7836b","parentId":"b0184e87","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:52:08.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! The user wants to use the `feishu-multi-agent-manager` skill to configure a multi-agent bot system. This skill is an interactive wizard that helps configure multiple agents with their Feishu app credentials.\n\nHowever, this skill needs to be invoked through the `main` function with specific actions. The skill itself is installed but it needs to be executed to use its wizard functionality.\n\nThe skill provides:\n1. An interactive wizard to configure multiple agents\n2. Tutorial for creating Feishu bots\n3. Batch creation support\n4. Preset role templates\n\nThe user needs to run through the wizard. Since I have the skill installed, I should explain how to use it and guide them through the process. But the skill's `main` function needs to be called with actions like `start_wizard`, `select_count`, etc.\n\nThe issue is that this skill is a TypeScript/Node.js package that needs to be executed, not a built-in skill that I can directly call. \n\nLet me check if I can find the source code or a way to invoke it. But the skill's code is in the `src` directory. I should guide the user on how to use this skill. The skill seems to need to be run via its entry point.\n\nActually, looking at the skill description, it says:\n```typescript\nawait main(ctx, { action: 'start_wizard' });\n```\n\nThis suggests this is a function that needs to be called. Since I'm an AI agent, I can't directly execute TypeScript code. However, the user might need to run this via a command or through the clawhub command.\n\nWait, I think I need to understand what the user is trying to do. They want to configure a multi-agent system using this skill. The skill itself is a guide/wizard that walks through the setup process. I should explain the steps and guide them through it, or if I can execute it, I should try to invoke the skill's wizard to help them configure it properly.","thinkingSignature":"ad9934f257040eacb754c0a657077727b8a6a42687bdf022cc963a4b05afdd6a"},{"type":"text","text":"了解！这个 skill 是「飞书多 Agent 配置助手」，帮你批量配置多个飞书机器人 Agent。让我看看它的源码结构，然后引导你完成配置。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q1mv03mb6ckr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-multi-agent-manager/src"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q1mv03mb6ckr_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-multi-agent-manager/README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7779,"output":527,"cacheRead":31568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39874,"cost":{"input":0.0023336999999999998,"output":0.0006324,"cacheRead":0.0018940799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0048601799999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775055112989,"responseId":"061c64092a0c980bd12005d6653f2b9a"}}
