{"type":"message","id":"2c79102c","parentId":"f072c904","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:53:18.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to configure just 1 bot - a \"selection agent\" (选品agent) that they already have running in the background. So they want to connect this existing agent (选品agent) to a Feishu bot so they can manage it through Feishu.\n\nLet me think about what they need:\n1. They have an existing \"selection agent\" running in the background\n2. They want to configure just 1 Feishu bot to manage this agent\n3. They need to create a Feishu app and get the App ID and App Secret\n\nSince it's just 1 bot, I need to guide them through:\n1. Creating a Feishu self-built app (if they haven't already)\n2. Getting the App ID and App Secret\n3. Configuring the bot with the correct settings\n\nBut wait - the user mentioned \"后台已经有的选品agent\" - this means there's already an agent running in the background (probably in OpenClaw). They want to connect this to a Feishu bot.\n\nI should ask if they already have a Feishu app created, or guide them through creating one and then configuring OpenClaw to connect to it.\n\nActually, let me ask a clarifying question - do they already have the Feishu app credentials (App ID and App Secret), or do they need to create a new Feishu app first?","thinkingSignature":"b42319ae15c9739a870d3209975b9025bddcd519cc1c2e00ee9ce58b1642db1b"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n明白！1 个 bot，连接到后台已有的**选品 Agent**。\n\n先确认一下：你说的\"后台已经有的选品 Agent\"，是指 OpenClaw 里已经跑着的某个 Agent 对吧？\n\n在开始之前，我需要知道：**你那边是否已经在飞书开放平台创建好了这个 Bot 的应用？**\n\n如果还没有，需要先创建；如果你已经有了 App ID 和 App Secret，直接给我，我来帮你配置到 `openclaw.json` 里。\n\n**创建飞书自建应用的基本步骤：**\n1. 去 https://open.feishu.cn/ 登录\n2. 创建企业自建应用 → 填写名称（比如\"选品助手\"）\n3. 进入「凭证与基础信息」→ 复制 **App ID** 和 **App Secret**\n4. 开启「机器人能力」\n5. 配置「事件订阅」→ 长连接模式 → 订阅 `im.message.receive_v1`\n6. 申请权限 → `im:message`、`im:chat`\n7. 发布应用\n\n你有已经创建好的应用了吗？还是需要我一步步教你创建？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","p