{"type":"message","id":"b32bc1b4","parentId":"29e9fcf6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:02:17.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The edit was successful. Now I need to tell the user what I did and that they need to restart the gateway for the changes to take effect.","thinkingSignature":"ad4d363cbdf16eac1ea2b8adf4028c602ed8d214746dde5d658e1a3698ffb320"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **配置完成！** 已做以下更新：\n\n1. **换上了新的 Feishu 凭证**（`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`）\n2. **启用了多账号格式**（accounts），绑定到 `tts` 这个 agent\n3. **添加了 binding**，让这个飞书 bot 连接到「选品专家」（tts）\n\n**接下来需要重启网关使配置生效：**\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启后，等待 1-2 分钟让 bot 自动连接飞书，然后在飞书里给这个 bot 发消息测试一下。告诉我结果如何！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":23494,"output":163,"cacheRead":31568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55225,"cost":{"input":0.007048199999999999,"output":0.00019559999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0018940799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00913788}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775055732040,"responseId":"061c6674f466b305120d2f80f93d2bc4"}}
